✅ **ALWAYS include dark mode variants** using `dark:` prefix
✅ **ALWAYS use responsive breakpoints** (`sm:`, `md:`, `lg:`, `xl:`)
✅ **Use custom utilities** from `index.css` when available (`menu-item`, `custom-scrollbar`)

